select  i_item_id
       ,i_item_desc 
       ,i_category 
       ,i_class 
       ,i_current_price
       ,sum(cs_ext_sales_price) as itemrevenue 
       ,sum(cs_ext_sales_price)*100/sum(sum(cs_ext_sales_price)) over
           (partition by i_class) as revenueratio
 from        catalog_sales
     ,item 
     ,date_dim
 where cs_item_sk = i_item_sk 
   and i_category in ('Jewelry', 'Sports', 'Books')
   and cs_sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
 and d_date between cast('2001-01-12' as date) 
                                 and (cast('2001-01-12' as date) + INTERVAL 5 day)
 group by i_item_id
         ,i_item_desc 
         ,i_category
         ,i_class
         ,i_current_price
 order by i_category
         ,i_class
         ,i_item_id
         ,i_item_desc
         ,revenueratio
limit 100

with my_customers as (
 select distinct c_customer_sk
        , c_current_addr_sk
 from   
        ( select cs_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 cs_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 cs_item_sk item_sk
          from   catalog_sales
          union all
          select ws_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 ws_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 ws_item_sk item_sk
          from   web_sales
         ) cs_or_ws_sales,
         item,
         date_dim,
         customer
 where   sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
         and item_sk = i_item_sk
         and i_category = 'Jewelry'
         and i_class = 'consignment'
         and c_customer_sk = cs_or_ws_sales.customer_sk
         and d_moy = 3
         and d_year = 1999
 )
 , my_revenue as (
 select c_customer_sk,
        sum(ss_ext_sales_price) as revenue
 from   my_customers,
        store_sales,
        customer_address,
        store,
        date_dim
 where  c_current_addr_sk = ca_address_sk
        and ca_county = s_county
        and ca_state = s_state
        and ss_sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
        and c_customer_sk = ss_customer_sk
        and d_month_seq between (select distinct d_month_seq+1
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
                           and  (select distinct d_month_seq+3
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
 group by c_customer_sk
 )
 , segments as
 (select cast((revenue/50) as int) as segment
  from   my_revenue
 )
  select  segment, count(*) as num_customers, segment*50 as segment_base
 from segments
 group by segment
 order by segment, num_customers
 limit 100

with ss as (
 select i_item_id,sum(ss_ext_sales_price) total_sales
 from
         store_sales,
         date_dim,
         customer_address,
         item
 where i_item_id in (select
     i_item_id
from item
where i_color in ('orchid','chiffon','lace'))
 and     ss_item_sk              = i_item_sk
 and     ss_sold_date_sk         = d_date_sk
 and     d_year                  = 2000
 and     d_moy                   = 1
 and     ss_addr_sk              = ca_address_sk
 and     ca_gmt_offset           = -8 
 group by i_item_id),
 cs as (
 select i_item_id,sum(cs_ext_sales_price) total_sales
 from
         catalog_sales,
         date_dim,
         customer_address,
         item
 where
         i_item_id               in (select
  i_item_id
from item
where i_color in ('orchid','chiffon','lace'))
 and     cs_item_sk              = i_item_sk
 and     cs_sold_date_sk         = d_date_sk
 and     d_year                  = 2000
 and     d_moy                   = 1
 and     cs_bill_addr_sk         = ca_address_sk
 and     ca_gmt_offset           = -8 
 group by i_item_id),
 ws as (
 select i_item_id,sum(ws_ext_sales_price) total_sales
 from
         web_sales,
         date_dim,
         customer_address,
         item
 where
         i_item_id               in (select
  i_item_id
from item
where i_color in ('orchid','chiffon','lace'))
 and     ws_item_sk              = i_item_sk
 and     ws_sold_date_sk         = d_date_sk
 and     d_year                  = 2000
 and     d_moy                   = 1
 and     ws_bill_addr_sk         = ca_address_sk
 and     ca_gmt_offset           = -8
 group by i_item_id)
  select  i_item_id ,sum(total_sales) total_sales
 from  (select * from ss 
        union all
        select * from cs 
        union all
        select * from ws) tmp1
 group by i_item_id
 order by total_sales,
          i_item_id
 limit 150

select
        cc_call_center_id Call_Center, sum(cr_net_loss) Returns_Loss,
        cc_name Call_Center_Name,
        cc_manager Manager
from         catalog_returns,
        call_center,
        date_dim,
        customer,
        customer_address,
        customer_demographics,
        household_demographics
where
        cr_call_center_sk       = cc_call_center_sk
and     cr_returned_date_sk     = d_date_sk
and     cr_returning_customer_sk= c_customer_sk
and     cd_demo_sk              = c_current_cdemo_sk
and     hd_demo_sk              = c_current_hdemo_sk
and     ca_address_sk           = c_current_addr_sk
and     d_year                  = 1999
and     d_moy                   = 11
and     ( (cd_marital_status       = 'M' and cd_education_status     = 'Unknown')
        or(cd_marital_status       = 'W' and cd_education_status     = 'Advanced Degree'))
and     hd_buy_potential like '0-500%'
and     ca_gmt_offset           = -7
group by cc_call_center_id,cc_name,cc_manager,cd_marital_status,cd_education_status
order by sum(cr_net_loss) desc limit 100

                      else 0 end) as inv_after

                 cs_item_sk item_sk
          from   catalog_sales
          union all
          select ws_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 ws_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 ws_item_sk item_sk
          from   web_sales

         and d_moy = 3
         and d_year = 1999

        sum(ss_ext_sales_price) as revenue

        store_sales,
        customer_address,
        store,
        date_dim
 where  c_current_addr_sk = ca_address_sk

with my_customers as (

 from   
        ( select cs_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 cs_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 cs_item_sk item_sk
          from   catalog_sales
          union all
          select ws_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 ws_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 ws_item_sk item_sk
          from   web_sales
         ) cs_or_ws_sales,
         item,
         date_dim,
         customer
 where   sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
         and item_sk = i_item_sk
         and i_category = 'Jewelry'
         and i_class = 'consignment'
         and c_customer_sk = cs_or_ws_sales.customer_sk
         and d_moy = 3
         and d_year = 1999
 )
 , my_revenue as (
 select c_customer_sk,
        sum(ss_ext_sales_price) as revenue
 from   my_customers,
        store_sales,
        customer_address,
        store,
        date_dim
 where  c_current_addr_sk = ca_address_sk
        and ca_county = s_county
        and ca_state = s_state

        and c_customer_sk = ss_customer_sk

                           and  (select distinct d_month_seq+3
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
 group by c_customer_sk

 , segments as
 (select cast((revenue/50) as int) as segment
  from   my_revenue

with my_customers as (
 select distinct c_customer_sk
        , c_current_addr_sk
 from   
        ( select cs_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 cs_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 cs_item_sk item_sk
          from   catalog_sales
          union all
          select ws_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 ws_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 ws_item_sk item_sk
          from   web_sales
         ) cs_or_ws_sales,
         item,
         date_dim,
         customer
 where   sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
         and item_sk = i_item_sk
         and i_category = 'Jewelry'
         and i_class = 'consignment'
         and c_customer_sk = cs_or_ws_sales.customer_sk
         and d_moy = 3
         and d_year = 1999
 )
 , my_revenue as (
 select c_customer_sk,
        sum(ss_ext_sales_price) as revenue
 from   my_customers,
        store_sales,
        customer_address,
        store,
        date_dim
 where  c_current_addr_sk = ca_address_sk
        and ca_county = s_county
        and ca_state = s_state
        and ss_sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
        and c_customer_sk = ss_customer_sk
        and d_month_seq between (select distinct d_month_seq+1
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
                           and  (select distinct d_month_seq+3
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
 group by c_customer_sk
 )
 , segments as
 (select cast((revenue/50) as int) as segment
  from   my_revenue
 )
  select  segment, count(*) as num_customers, segment*50 as segment_base
 from segments
 group by segment
 order by segment, num_customers
 limit 100

select  *
 from(select w_warehouse_name
            ,i_item_id
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) < cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                        then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_before
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) >= cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                      then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_after
   from inventory
       ,warehouse
       ,item
       ,date_dim
   where i_current_price between 0.99 and 1.49
     and i_item_sk          = inv_item_sk
     and inv_warehouse_sk   = w_warehouse_sk
     and inv_date_sk    = d_date_sk
     and d_date between (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) - INTERVAL '30' day)
                    and (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) + INTERVAL '30' day)
   group by w_warehouse_name, i_item_id) x
 where (case when inv_before > 0
             then inv_after / inv_before
             else null
             end) between 2.0/3.0 and 3.0/2.0
 order by w_warehouse_name
         ,i_item_id
 limit 200

with my_customers as (
 select distinct c_customer_sk
        , c_current_addr_sk
 from   
        ( select cs_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 cs_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 cs_item_sk item_sk
          from   catalog_sales
          union all
          select ws_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 ws_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 ws_item_sk item_sk
          from   web_sales
         ) cs_or_ws_sales,
         item,
         date_dim,
         customer
 where   sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
         and item_sk = i_item_sk
         and i_category = 'Jewelry'
         and i_class = 'consignment'
         and c_customer_sk = cs_or_ws_sales.customer_sk
         and d_moy = 3
         and d_year = 1999
 )
 , my_revenue as (
 select c_customer_sk,
        sum(ss_ext_sales_price) as revenue
 from   my_customers,
        store_sales,
        customer_address,
        store,
        date_dim
 where  c_current_addr_sk = ca_address_sk
        and ca_county = s_county
        and ca_state = s_state
        and ss_sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
        and c_customer_sk = ss_customer_sk
        and d_month_seq between (select distinct d_month_seq+1
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
                           and  (select distinct d_month_seq+3
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
 group by c_customer_sk
 )
 , segments as
 (select cast((revenue/50) as int) as segment
  from   my_revenue
 )
  select  segment, segment*50 as segment_base, count(*) as num_customers
 from segments
 group by segment
 order by segment, num_customers
 limit 120

            ,i_item_id

                        then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_before
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) >= cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                      then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_after
   from inventory
       ,warehouse
       ,item
       ,date_dim
   where i_current_price between 0.99 and 1.49
     and i_item_sk          = inv_item_sk
     and inv_warehouse_sk   = w_warehouse_sk
     and inv_date_sk    = d_date_sk
     and d_date between (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) - INTERVAL '30' day)
                    and (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) + INTERVAL '30' day)
   group by w_warehouse_name, i_item_id) x
 where (case when inv_before > 0
             then inv_after / inv_before
             else null
             end) between 2.0/3.0 and 3.0/2.0
 order by w_warehouse_name
         ,i_item_id
 limit 200

                        then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_before
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) >= cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                      then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_after
   from inventory
       ,warehouse
       ,item
       ,date_dim
   where i_current_price between 0.99 and 1.49
     and i_item_sk          = inv_item_sk
     and inv_warehouse_sk   = w_warehouse_sk
     and inv_date_sk    = d_date_sk

                    and (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) + INTERVAL '30' day)
   group by w_warehouse_name, i_item_id) x
 where (case when inv_before > 0
             then inv_after / inv_before
             else null
             end) between 2.0/3.0 and 3.0/2.0
 order by w_warehouse_name
         ,i_item_id
 limit 100

select  *
 from(select w_warehouse_name
            ,i_item_id
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) < cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                        then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_before
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) >= cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                      then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_after
   from inventory
       ,warehouse
       ,item
       ,date_dim
   where i_current_price between 0.99 and 1.49
     and i_item_sk          = inv_item_sk
     and inv_warehouse_sk   = w_warehouse_sk
     and inv_date_sk    = d_date_sk
     and d_date between (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) - INTERVAL '30' day)
                    and (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) + INTERVAL '30' day)
   group by w_warehouse_name, i_item_id) x
 where (case when inv_before > 0
             then inv_after / inv_before
             else null
             end) between 2.0/3.0 and 3.0/2.0
 order by w_warehouse_name
         ,i_item_id
 limit 200

select  *
 from(select w_warehouse_name
            ,i_item_id
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) < cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                        then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_before
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) >= cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                      then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_after
   from inventory
       ,warehouse
       ,item
       ,date_dim
   where i_current_price between 0.99 and 1.49
     and i_item_sk          = inv_item_sk
     and inv_warehouse_sk   = w_warehouse_sk
     and inv_date_sk    = d_date_sk
     and d_date between (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) - INTERVAL '30' day)
                    and (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) + INTERVAL '30' day)
   group by w_warehouse_name, i_item_id) x
 where (case when inv_before > 0
             then inv_after / inv_before
             else null
             end) between 2.0/3.0 and 3.0/2.0
 order by w_warehouse_name
         ,i_item_id
 limit 100

       ,c_salutation
       ,ss_ticket_number
,c_preferred_cust_flag 
       ,cnt from
   (select ss_ticket_number
          ,ss_customer_sk
          ,count(*) cnt
    from store_sales,date_dim,store,household_demographics
    where store_sales.ss_sold_date_sk = date_dim.d_date_sk
    and store_sales.ss_store_sk = store.s_store_sk  
    and store_sales.ss_hdemo_sk = household_demographics.hd_demo_sk
    and date_dim.d_dom between 1 and 2 
    and (household_demographics.hd_buy_potential = '>10000' or
         household_demographics.hd_buy_potential = 'Unknown')
    and household_demographics.hd_vehicle_count > 0
    and case when household_demographics.hd_vehicle_count > 0 then 
             household_demographics.hd_dep_count/ household_demographics.hd_vehicle_count else null end > 1
    and date_dim.d_year in (2000,2000+1,2000+2)
    and store.s_county in ('Mobile County','Maverick County','Huron County','Kittitas County')
    group by ss_ticket_number,ss_customer_sk) dj,customer
    where ss_customer_sk = c_customer_sk
      and cnt between 1 and 5
    order by cnt desc, c_last_name asc limit 100

                 cs_item_sk item_sk
          from   catalog_sales

                 ws_item_sk item_sk
          from   web_sales

         and d_moy = 3
         and d_year = 1999

        store_sales,
        customer_address,
        store,
        date_dim

select  *
 from(select w_warehouse_name
            ,i_item_id
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) < cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                        then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_before
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) >= cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                      then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_after
   from inventory
       ,warehouse
       ,item
       ,date_dim
   where i_current_price between 0.99 and 1.49
     and i_item_sk          = inv_item_sk
     and inv_warehouse_sk   = w_warehouse_sk
     and inv_date_sk    = d_date_sk
     and d_date between (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) - INTERVAL '30' day)
                    and (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) + INTERVAL '30' day)
   group by w_warehouse_name, i_item_id) x
 where (case when inv_before > 0
             then inv_after / inv_before
             else null
             end) between 2.0/3.0 and 3.0/2.0
 order by w_warehouse_name
         ,i_item_id
 limit 110

with my_customers as (
 select distinct c_customer_sk
        , c_current_addr_sk
 from   
        ( select cs_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 cs_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 cs_item_sk item_sk
          from   catalog_sales
          union all
          select ws_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 ws_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 ws_item_sk item_sk
          from   web_sales
         ) cs_or_ws_sales,
         item,
         date_dim,
         customer
 where   sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
         and item_sk = i_item_sk
         and i_category = 'Jewelry'
         and i_class = 'consignment'
         and c_customer_sk = cs_or_ws_sales.customer_sk
         and d_moy = 3
         and d_year = 1999
 )
 , my_revenue as (
 select c_customer_sk,
        sum(ss_ext_sales_price) as revenue
 from   my_customers,
        store_sales,
        customer_address,
        store,
        date_dim
 where  c_current_addr_sk = ca_address_sk
        and ca_county = s_county
        and ca_state = s_state
        and ss_sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
        and c_customer_sk = ss_customer_sk
        and d_month_seq between (select distinct d_month_seq+1
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
                           and  (select distinct d_month_seq+3
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
 group by c_customer_sk
 )
 , segments as
 (select cast((revenue/50) as int) as segment
  from   my_revenue
 )
  select  segment, count(*) as num_customers, segment*50 as segment_base
 from segments
 group by segment
 order by segment, num_customers
 limit 100

                 cs_item_sk item_sk
          from   catalog_sales
          union all
          select ws_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 ws_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 ws_item_sk item_sk
          from   web_sales
         ) cs_or_ws_sales,
         item,

         and i_class = 'consignment'
         and c_customer_sk = cs_or_ws_sales.customer_sk
         and d_moy = 3
         and d_year = 1999
 )
 , my_revenue as (
 select c_customer_sk,
        sum(ss_ext_sales_price) as revenue
 from   my_customers,
        store_sales,
        customer_address,
        store,
        date_dim
 where  c_current_addr_sk = ca_address_sk
        and ca_county = s_county
        and ca_state = s_state
        and ss_sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
        and c_customer_sk = ss_customer_sk
        and d_month_seq between (select distinct d_month_seq+1
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
                           and  (select distinct d_month_seq+3
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
 group by c_customer_sk

 , segments as
 (select cast((revenue/50) as int) as segment
  from   my_revenue

                        then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_before
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) >= cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                      then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_after
   from inventory
       ,warehouse
       ,item
       ,date_dim
   where i_current_price between 0.99 and 1.49
     and i_item_sk          = inv_item_sk
     and inv_warehouse_sk   = w_warehouse_sk

     and d_date between (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) - INTERVAL '30' day)
                    and (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) + INTERVAL '30' day)
   group by w_warehouse_name, i_item_id) x
 where (case when inv_before > 0
             then inv_after / inv_before
             else null
             end) between 2.0/3.0 and 3.0/2.0
 order by w_warehouse_name
         ,i_item_id
 limit 110

with my_customers as (
 select distinct c_customer_sk
        , c_current_addr_sk
 from   
        ( select cs_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 cs_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 cs_item_sk item_sk
          from   catalog_sales
          union all
          select ws_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 ws_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 ws_item_sk item_sk
          from   web_sales
         ) cs_or_ws_sales,
         item,
         date_dim,
         customer
 where   sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
         and item_sk = i_item_sk
         and i_category = 'Jewelry'
         and i_class = 'consignment'
         and c_customer_sk = cs_or_ws_sales.customer_sk
         and d_moy = 3
         and d_year = 1999
 )
 , my_revenue as (
 select c_customer_sk,
        sum(ss_ext_sales_price) as revenue
 from   my_customers,
        store_sales,
        customer_address,
        store,
        date_dim
 where  c_current_addr_sk = ca_address_sk
        and ca_county = s_county
        and ca_state = s_state
        and ss_sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
        and c_customer_sk = ss_customer_sk
        and d_month_seq between (select distinct d_month_seq+1
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
                           and  (select distinct d_month_seq+3
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
 group by c_customer_sk
 )
 , segments as
 (select cast((revenue/50) as int) as segment
  from   my_revenue
 )
  select  segment*50 as segment_base, segment, count(*) as num_customers
 from segments
 group by segment
 order by segment, num_customers
 limit 100

            ,i_item_id
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) < cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                        then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_before
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) >= cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                      then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_after
   from inventory
       ,warehouse
       ,item
       ,date_dim

     and i_item_sk          = inv_item_sk
     and inv_warehouse_sk   = w_warehouse_sk

                    and (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) + INTERVAL '30' day)
   group by w_warehouse_name, i_item_id) x
 where (case when inv_before > 0
             then inv_after / inv_before
             else null
             end) between 2.0/3.0 and 3.0/2.0
 order by w_warehouse_name
         ,i_item_id
 limit 100

                      then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_after
   from inventory

         ,i_item_id

                 cs_item_sk item_sk
          from   catalog_sales
          union all
          select ws_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 ws_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 ws_item_sk item_sk
          from   web_sales
         ) cs_or_ws_sales,
         item,

         customer

         and i_class = 'consignment'
         and c_customer_sk = cs_or_ws_sales.customer_sk
         and d_moy = 3
         and d_year = 1999
 )
 , my_revenue as (
 select c_customer_sk,
        sum(ss_ext_sales_price) as revenue
 from   my_customers,
        store_sales,
        customer_address,
        store,
        date_dim
 where  c_current_addr_sk = ca_address_sk
        and ca_county = s_county
        and ca_state = s_state

        and c_customer_sk = ss_customer_sk

                           and  (select distinct d_month_seq+3
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)

 , segments as

  from   my_revenue

            ,i_item_id
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) < cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                        then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_before
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) >= cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                      then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_after
   from inventory
       ,warehouse
       ,item
       ,date_dim
   where i_current_price between 0.99 and 1.49
     and i_item_sk          = inv_item_sk
     and inv_warehouse_sk   = w_warehouse_sk
     and inv_date_sk    = d_date_sk

                    and (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) + INTERVAL '30' day)
   group by w_warehouse_name, i_item_id) x
 where (case when inv_before > 0
             then inv_after / inv_before
             else null
             end) between 2.0/3.0 and 3.0/2.0
 order by w_warehouse_name
         ,i_item_id
 limit 100

 from

                 cs_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 cs_item_sk item_sk
          from   catalog_sales
          union all
          select ws_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 ws_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 ws_item_sk item_sk
          from   web_sales
         ) cs_or_ws_sales,
         item,
         date_dim,
         customer
 where   sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
         and item_sk = i_item_sk
         and i_category = 'Jewelry'
         and i_class = 'consignment'
         and c_customer_sk = cs_or_ws_sales.customer_sk
         and d_moy = 3
         and d_year = 1999
 )
 , my_revenue as (
 select c_customer_sk,
        sum(ss_ext_sales_price) as revenue
 from   my_customers,
        store_sales,
        customer_address,
        store,
        date_dim
 where  c_current_addr_sk = ca_address_sk
        and ca_county = s_county
        and ca_state = s_state
        and ss_sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
        and c_customer_sk = ss_customer_sk
        and d_month_seq between (select distinct d_month_seq+1
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
                           and  (select distinct d_month_seq+3
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
 group by c_customer_sk
 )
 , segments as
 (select cast((revenue/50) as int) as segment
  from   my_revenue
 )
  select  segment*50 as segment_base, segment, count(*) as num_customers
 from segments
 group by segment
 order by segment, num_customers
 limit 100

            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) >= cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                      then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_after

       ,item

     and inv_warehouse_sk   = w_warehouse_sk

                    and (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) + INTERVAL '30' day)
   group by w_warehouse_name, i_item_id) x
 where (case when inv_before > 0
             then inv_after / inv_before

         ,i_item_id
 limit 200

                 cs_item_sk item_sk
          from   catalog_sales
          union all

                 ws_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 ws_item_sk item_sk
          from   web_sales

         and d_moy = 3
         and d_year = 1999

 , my_revenue as (

        sum(ss_ext_sales_price) as revenue
 from   my_customers,
        store_sales,
        customer_address,
        store,
        date_dim
 where  c_current_addr_sk = ca_address_sk
        and ca_county = s_county
        and ca_state = s_state

                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)

 , segments as
 (select cast((revenue/50) as int) as segment
  from   my_revenue

                 cs_item_sk item_sk
          from   catalog_sales
          union all
          select ws_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 ws_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 ws_item_sk item_sk
          from   web_sales
         ) cs_or_ws_sales,
         item,
         date_dim,
         customer

         and i_class = 'consignment'
         and c_customer_sk = cs_or_ws_sales.customer_sk
         and d_moy = 3
         and d_year = 1999
 )
 , my_revenue as (
 select c_customer_sk,
        sum(ss_ext_sales_price) as revenue
 from   my_customers,
        store_sales,
        customer_address,
        store,
        date_dim
 where  c_current_addr_sk = ca_address_sk
        and ca_county = s_county
        and ca_state = s_state
        and ss_sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
        and c_customer_sk = ss_customer_sk
        and d_month_seq between (select distinct d_month_seq+1
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
                           and  (select distinct d_month_seq+3
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
 group by c_customer_sk
 )
 , segments as
 (select cast((revenue/50) as int) as segment
  from   my_revenue
 )
  select  segment*50 as segment_base, segment, count(*) as num_customers
 from segments
 group by segment

 limit 100

with my_customers as (
 select distinct c_customer_sk
        , c_current_addr_sk
 from   
        ( select cs_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 cs_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 cs_item_sk item_sk
          from   catalog_sales
          union all
          select ws_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 ws_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 ws_item_sk item_sk
          from   web_sales
         ) cs_or_ws_sales,
         item,
         date_dim,
         customer
 where   sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
         and item_sk = i_item_sk
         and i_category = 'Jewelry'
         and i_class = 'consignment'
         and c_customer_sk = cs_or_ws_sales.customer_sk
         and d_moy = 3
         and d_year = 1999
 )
 , my_revenue as (
 select c_customer_sk,
        sum(ss_ext_sales_price) as revenue
 from   my_customers,
        store_sales,
        customer_address,
        store,
        date_dim
 where  c_current_addr_sk = ca_address_sk
        and ca_county = s_county
        and ca_state = s_state
        and ss_sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
        and c_customer_sk = ss_customer_sk
        and d_month_seq between (select distinct d_month_seq+1
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
                           and  (select distinct d_month_seq+3
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
 group by c_customer_sk
 )
 , segments as
 (select cast((revenue/50) as int) as segment
  from   my_revenue
 )
  select  segment*50 as segment_base, segment, count(*) as num_customers
 from segments
 group by segment
 order by segment, num_customers
 limit 100

select  *

            ,i_item_id
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) < cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                        then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_before
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) >= cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                      then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_after
   from inventory
       ,warehouse
       ,item
       ,date_dim
   where i_current_price between 0.99 and 1.49
     and i_item_sk          = inv_item_sk
     and inv_warehouse_sk   = w_warehouse_sk
     and inv_date_sk    = d_date_sk
     and d_date between (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) - INTERVAL '30' day)
                    and (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) + INTERVAL '30' day)
   group by w_warehouse_name, i_item_id) x
 where (case when inv_before > 0
             then inv_after / inv_before
             else null
             end) between 2.0/3.0 and 3.0/2.0
 order by w_warehouse_name
         ,i_item_id
 limit 200

with my_customers as (

        , c_current_addr_sk
 from   
        ( select cs_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 cs_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 cs_item_sk item_sk
          from   catalog_sales
          union all
          select ws_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 ws_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 ws_item_sk item_sk
          from   web_sales
         ) cs_or_ws_sales,
         item,
         date_dim,
         customer
 where   sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
         and item_sk = i_item_sk
         and i_category = 'Jewelry'
         and i_class = 'consignment'
         and c_customer_sk = cs_or_ws_sales.customer_sk
         and d_moy = 3
         and d_year = 1999
 )
 , my_revenue as (
 select c_customer_sk,
        sum(ss_ext_sales_price) as revenue
 from   my_customers,
        store_sales,
        customer_address,
        store,
        date_dim
 where  c_current_addr_sk = ca_address_sk
        and ca_county = s_county
        and ca_state = s_state
        and ss_sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
        and c_customer_sk = ss_customer_sk
        and d_month_seq between (select distinct d_month_seq+1
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
                           and  (select distinct d_month_seq+3
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
 group by c_customer_sk
 )
 , segments as
 (select cast((revenue/50) as int) as segment
  from   my_revenue
 )

 from segments
 group by segment

 limit 100

select  *
 from(select w_warehouse_name
            ,i_item_id
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) < cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                        then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_before
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) >= cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                      then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_after
   from inventory
       ,warehouse
       ,item
       ,date_dim
   where i_current_price between 0.99 and 1.49
     and i_item_sk          = inv_item_sk
     and inv_warehouse_sk   = w_warehouse_sk
     and inv_date_sk    = d_date_sk
     and d_date between (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) - INTERVAL '30' day)
                    and (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) + INTERVAL '30' day)
   group by w_warehouse_name, i_item_id) x
 where (case when inv_before > 0

                      else 0 end) as inv_after
   from inventory

 where (case when inv_before > 0
             then inv_after / inv_before

 limit 110

            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) < cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                        then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_before
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) >= cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                      then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_after
   from inventory
       ,warehouse
       ,item
       ,date_dim
   where i_current_price between 0.99 and 1.49
     and i_item_sk          = inv_item_sk
     and inv_warehouse_sk   = w_warehouse_sk
     and inv_date_sk    = d_date_sk
     and d_date between (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) - INTERVAL '30' day)
                    and (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) + INTERVAL '30' day)
   group by w_warehouse_name, i_item_id) x
 where (case when inv_before > 0
             then inv_after / inv_before
             else null
             end) between 2.0/3.0 and 3.0/2.0
 order by w_warehouse_name
         ,i_item_id
 limit 110

        ( select cs_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 cs_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 cs_item_sk item_sk
          from   catalog_sales
          union all
          select ws_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 ws_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 ws_item_sk item_sk
          from   web_sales
         ) cs_or_ws_sales,
         item,
         date_dim,
         customer
 where   sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
         and item_sk = i_item_sk
         and i_category = 'Jewelry'
         and i_class = 'consignment'
         and c_customer_sk = cs_or_ws_sales.customer_sk
         and d_moy = 3
         and d_year = 1999
 )
 , my_revenue as (
 select c_customer_sk,
        sum(ss_ext_sales_price) as revenue
 from   my_customers,
        store_sales,
        customer_address,
        store,
        date_dim
 where  c_current_addr_sk = ca_address_sk
        and ca_county = s_county
        and ca_state = s_state
        and ss_sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
        and c_customer_sk = ss_customer_sk
        and d_month_seq between (select distinct d_month_seq+1
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
                           and  (select distinct d_month_seq+3
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
 group by c_customer_sk
 )
 , segments as
 (select cast((revenue/50) as int) as segment
  from   my_revenue
 )
  select  segment, segment*50 as segment_base, count(*) as num_customers
 from segments
 group by segment
 order by segment, num_customers
 limit 120

       ,ss_ticket_number
       ,cnt from

          ,ss_customer_sk
          ,count(*) cnt
    from store_sales,date_dim,store,household_demographics
    where store_sales.ss_sold_date_sk = date_dim.d_date_sk
    and store_sales.ss_store_sk = store.s_store_sk  
    and store_sales.ss_hdemo_sk = household_demographics.hd_demo_sk
    and date_dim.d_dom between 1 and 2 
    and (household_demographics.hd_buy_potential = '>10000' or
         household_demographics.hd_buy_potential = 'Unknown')
    and household_demographics.hd_vehicle_count > 0
    and case when household_demographics.hd_vehicle_count > 0 then 
             household_demographics.hd_dep_count/ household_demographics.hd_vehicle_count else null end > 1
    and date_dim.d_year in (2000,2000+1,2000+2)
    and store.s_county in ('Mobile County','Maverick County','Huron County','Kittitas County')
    group by ss_ticket_number,ss_customer_sk) dj,customer
    where ss_customer_sk = c_customer_sk
      and cnt between 1 and 5
    order by cnt desc, c_last_name asc limit 100

with my_customers as (

                 cs_item_sk item_sk
          from   catalog_sales
          union all

                 ws_item_sk item_sk

select  *
 from(select w_warehouse_name
            ,i_item_id
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) < cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                        then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_before
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) >= cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                      then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_after
   from inventory
       ,warehouse
       ,item
       ,date_dim
   where i_current_price between 0.99 and 1.49
     and i_item_sk          = inv_item_sk
     and inv_warehouse_sk   = w_warehouse_sk
     and inv_date_sk    = d_date_sk
     and d_date between (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) - INTERVAL '30' day)
                    and (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) + INTERVAL '30' day)
   group by w_warehouse_name, i_item_id) x
 where (case when inv_before > 0
             then inv_after / inv_before
             else null
             end) between 2.0/3.0 and 3.0/2.0
 order by w_warehouse_name
         ,i_item_id
 limit 110

         and i_category = 'Jewelry'
         and i_class = 'consignment'

         and d_moy = 3
         and d_year = 1999

 select c_customer_sk,
        sum(ss_ext_sales_price) as revenue
 from   my_customers,
        store_sales,
        customer_address,
        store,
        date_dim
 where  c_current_addr_sk = ca_address_sk
        and ca_county = s_county
        and ca_state = s_state

                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
 group by c_customer_sk

 , segments as

select  *
 from(select w_warehouse_name
            ,i_item_id
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) < cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                        then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_before
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) >= cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                      then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_after
   from inventory
       ,warehouse
       ,item
       ,date_dim
   where i_current_price between 0.99 and 1.49
     and i_item_sk          = inv_item_sk
     and inv_warehouse_sk   = w_warehouse_sk
     and inv_date_sk    = d_date_sk
     and d_date between (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) - INTERVAL '30' day)
                    and (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) + INTERVAL '30' day)
   group by w_warehouse_name, i_item_id) x
 where (case when inv_before > 0
             then inv_after / inv_before
             else null
             end) between 2.0/3.0 and 3.0/2.0
 order by w_warehouse_name
         ,i_item_id
 limit 110

 group by i_manufact_id),

          i_item_id,sum(cs_ext_sales_price) total_sales
 from
         catalog_sales,
         date_dim,
         customer_address,
         item
 where
         i_item_id               in (select
  i_item_id
from
 item
where i_category in ('Children'))
 and     cs_item_sk              = i_item_sk
 and     cs_sold_date_sk         = d_date_sk
 and     d_year                  = 1999
 and     d_moy                   = 9
 and     cs_bill_addr_sk         = ca_address_sk
 and     ca_gmt_offset           = -6 
 group by i_item_id),
 ws as (
 select
          i_item_id,sum(ws_ext_sales_price) total_sales
 from
         web_sales,
         date_dim,
         customer_address,
         item
 where
         i_item_id               in (select
  i_item_id
from
 item
where i_category in ('Children'))
 and     ws_item_sk              = i_item_sk
 and     ws_sold_date_sk         = d_date_sk
 and     d_year                  = 1999
 and     d_moy                   = 9
 and     ws_bill_addr_sk         = ca_address_sk
 and     ca_gmt_offset           = -6
 group by i_item_id)
  select   sum(total_sales) total_sales,
  i_item_id
 from  (select * from ss 
        union all
        select * from cs 
        union all
        select * from ws) tmp1
 group by i_item_id
 order by i_item_id
      ,total_sales
 limit 100

select i_brand_id brand_id, i_brand brand,t_minute, t_hour,
         sum(ext_price) ext_price
 from item, (select ws_ext_sales_price as ext_price, 
                        ws_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        ws_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        ws_sold_time_sk as time_sk  
                 from web_sales,date_dim
                 where d_date_sk = ws_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2000
                 union all
                 select cs_ext_sales_price as ext_price,
                        cs_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        cs_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        cs_sold_time_sk as time_sk
                 from catalog_sales,date_dim
                 where d_date_sk = cs_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2000
                 union all
                 select ss_ext_sales_price as ext_price,
                        ss_sold_date_sk as sold_date_sk,
                        ss_item_sk as sold_item_sk,
                        ss_sold_time_sk as time_sk
                 from store_sales,date_dim
                 where d_date_sk = ss_sold_date_sk
                   and d_moy=12
                   and d_year=2000
                 ) tmp,time_dim
 where
   sold_item_sk = i_item_sk
   and i_manager_id=1
   and time_sk = t_time_sk
   and (t_meal_time = 'breakfast' or t_meal_time = 'dinner')
 group by i_brand, i_brand_id,t_hour,t_minute
 order by ext_price desc, i_brand_id
 limit 100

with my_customers as (
 select distinct c_customer_sk
        , c_current_addr_sk
 from   
        ( select cs_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 cs_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 cs_item_sk item_sk
          from   catalog_sales
          union all
          select ws_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 ws_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 ws_item_sk item_sk
          from   web_sales
         ) cs_or_ws_sales,
         item,
         date_dim,
         customer
 where   sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
         and item_sk = i_item_sk
         and i_category = 'Jewelry'
         and i_class = 'consignment'
         and c_customer_sk = cs_or_ws_sales.customer_sk
         and d_moy = 3
         and d_year = 1999
 )
 , my_revenue as (
 select c_customer_sk,
        sum(ss_ext_sales_price) as revenue
 from   my_customers,
        store_sales,
        customer_address,
        store,
        date_dim
 where  c_current_addr_sk = ca_address_sk
        and ca_county = s_county
        and ca_state = s_state
        and ss_sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
        and c_customer_sk = ss_customer_sk
        and d_month_seq between (select distinct d_month_seq+1
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
                           and  (select distinct d_month_seq+3
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
 group by c_customer_sk
 )
 , segments as
 (select cast((revenue/50) as int) as segment
  from   my_revenue
 )
  select  segment*50 as segment_base, segment, count(*) as num_customers
 from segments
 group by segment
 order by segment, num_customers
 limit 100

select c_last_name
       ,c_first_name
       ,c_salutation
       ,ss_ticket_number
,c_preferred_cust_flag 
       ,cnt from
   (select ss_ticket_number
          ,ss_customer_sk
          ,count(*) cnt
    from store_sales,date_dim,store,household_demographics
    where store_sales.ss_sold_date_sk = date_dim.d_date_sk
    and store_sales.ss_store_sk = store.s_store_sk  
    and store_sales.ss_hdemo_sk = household_demographics.hd_demo_sk
    and date_dim.d_dom between 1 and 2 
    and (household_demographics.hd_buy_potential = '>10000' or
         household_demographics.hd_buy_potential = 'Unknown')
    and household_demographics.hd_vehicle_count > 0
    and case when household_demographics.hd_vehicle_count > 0 then 
             household_demographics.hd_dep_count/ household_demographics.hd_vehicle_count else null end > 1
    and date_dim.d_year in (2000,2000+1,2000+2)
    and store.s_county in ('Mobile County','Maverick County','Huron County','Kittitas County')
    group by ss_ticket_number,ss_customer_sk) dj,customer
    where ss_customer_sk = c_customer_sk
      and cnt between 1 and 5
    order by cnt desc, c_last_name asc limit 100

                      else 0 end) as inv_after

with my_customers as (
 select distinct c_customer_sk
        , c_current_addr_sk
 from   
        ( select cs_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 cs_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 cs_item_sk item_sk
          from   catalog_sales
          union all
          select ws_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 ws_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 ws_item_sk item_sk
          from   web_sales
         ) cs_or_ws_sales,
         item,
         date_dim,
         customer
 where   sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
         and item_sk = i_item_sk
         and i_category = 'Jewelry'
         and i_class = 'consignment'
         and c_customer_sk = cs_or_ws_sales.customer_sk
         and d_moy = 3
         and d_year = 1999
 )
 , my_revenue as (
 select c_customer_sk,
        sum(ss_ext_sales_price) as revenue
 from   my_customers,
        store_sales,
        customer_address,
        store,
        date_dim
 where  c_current_addr_sk = ca_address_sk
        and ca_county = s_county
        and ca_state = s_state
        and ss_sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
        and c_customer_sk = ss_customer_sk
        and d_month_seq between (select distinct d_month_seq+1
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
                           and  (select distinct d_month_seq+3
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
 group by c_customer_sk
 )
 , segments as
 (select cast((revenue/50) as int) as segment
  from   my_revenue
 )
  select  segment, count(*) as num_customers, segment*50 as segment_base
 from segments
 group by segment
 order by segment, num_customers
 limit 100

                      else 0 end) as inv_after

 where (case when inv_before > 0
             then inv_after / inv_before
             else null

 order by w_warehouse_name
         ,i_item_id
 limit 100

select c_first_name, c_last_name
       ,c_salutation
       ,c_preferred_cust_flag 
       ,ss_ticket_number
       ,cnt from
   (select ss_ticket_number
          ,ss_customer_sk
          ,count(*) cnt
    from store_sales,date_dim,store,household_demographics
    where store_sales.ss_sold_date_sk = date_dim.d_date_sk
    and store_sales.ss_store_sk = store.s_store_sk  
    and store_sales.ss_hdemo_sk = household_demographics.hd_demo_sk
    and date_dim.d_dom between 1 and 2 
    and (household_demographics.hd_buy_potential = '>10000' or
         household_demographics.hd_buy_potential = 'Unknown')
    and household_demographics.hd_vehicle_count > 0
    and case when household_demographics.hd_vehicle_count > 0 then 
             household_demographics.hd_dep_count/ household_demographics.hd_vehicle_count else null end > 1
    and date_dim.d_year in (2000,2000+1,2000+2)
    and store.s_county in ('Mobile County','Maverick County','Huron County','Kittitas County')
    group by ss_ticket_number,ss_customer_sk) dj,customer
    where ss_customer_sk = c_customer_sk
      and cnt between 1 and 5
    order by cnt desc, c_last_name asc limit 100

with my_customers as (
 select distinct c_customer_sk
        , c_current_addr_sk
 from   
        ( select cs_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 cs_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 cs_item_sk item_sk
          from   catalog_sales
          union all
          select ws_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 ws_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 ws_item_sk item_sk
          from   web_sales
         ) cs_or_ws_sales,
         item,
         date_dim,
         customer
 where   sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
         and item_sk = i_item_sk
         and i_category = 'Jewelry'
         and i_class = 'consignment'
         and c_customer_sk = cs_or_ws_sales.customer_sk
         and d_moy = 3
         and d_year = 1999
 )
 , my_revenue as (
 select c_customer_sk,
        sum(ss_ext_sales_price) as revenue
 from   my_customers,
        store_sales,
        customer_address,
        store,
        date_dim
 where  c_current_addr_sk = ca_address_sk
        and ca_county = s_county
        and ca_state = s_state
        and ss_sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
        and c_customer_sk = ss_customer_sk
        and d_month_seq between (select distinct d_month_seq+1
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
                           and  (select distinct d_month_seq+3
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
 group by c_customer_sk
 )
 , segments as
 (select cast((revenue/50) as int) as segment
  from   my_revenue
 )
  select  segment, segment*50 as segment_base, count(*) as num_customers
 from segments
 group by segment
 order by segment, num_customers
 limit 120

            ,i_item_id
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) < cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                        then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_before
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) >= cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                      then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_after
   from inventory
       ,warehouse
       ,item
       ,date_dim
   where i_current_price between 0.99 and 1.49
     and i_item_sk          = inv_item_sk
     and inv_warehouse_sk   = w_warehouse_sk
     and inv_date_sk    = d_date_sk
     and d_date between (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) - INTERVAL '30' day)
                    and (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) + INTERVAL '30' day)
   group by w_warehouse_name, i_item_id) x
 where (case when inv_before > 0
             then inv_after / inv_before
             else null
             end) between 2.0/3.0 and 3.0/2.0
 order by w_warehouse_name
         ,i_item_id
 limit 110

select  *
 from(select w_warehouse_name
            ,i_item_id
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) < cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                        then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_before
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) >= cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                      then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_after
   from inventory
       ,warehouse
       ,item
       ,date_dim
   where i_current_price between 0.99 and 1.49
     and i_item_sk          = inv_item_sk
     and inv_warehouse_sk   = w_warehouse_sk
     and inv_date_sk    = d_date_sk
     and d_date between (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) - INTERVAL '30' day)
                    and (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) + INTERVAL '30' day)
   group by w_warehouse_name, i_item_id) x
 where (case when inv_before > 0
             then inv_after / inv_before
             else null
             end) between 2.0/3.0 and 3.0/2.0
 order by w_warehouse_name
         ,i_item_id
 limit 200

select  *
 from(select w_warehouse_name
            ,i_item_id
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) < cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                        then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_before
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) >= cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                      then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_after
   from inventory
       ,warehouse
       ,item
       ,date_dim
   where i_current_price between 0.99 and 1.49
     and i_item_sk          = inv_item_sk
     and inv_warehouse_sk   = w_warehouse_sk
     and inv_date_sk    = d_date_sk
     and d_date between (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) - INTERVAL '30' day)
                    and (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) + INTERVAL '30' day)
   group by w_warehouse_name, i_item_id) x
 where (case when inv_before > 0
             then inv_after / inv_before
             else null
             end) between 2.0/3.0 and 3.0/2.0
 order by w_warehouse_name
         ,i_item_id
 limit 200

            ,i_item_id
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) < cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                        then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_before
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) >= cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                      then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_after
   from inventory
       ,warehouse
       ,item
       ,date_dim
   where i_current_price between 0.99 and 1.49
     and i_item_sk          = inv_item_sk
     and inv_warehouse_sk   = w_warehouse_sk
     and inv_date_sk    = d_date_sk
     and d_date between (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) - INTERVAL '30' day)
                    and (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) + INTERVAL '30' day)
   group by w_warehouse_name, i_item_id) x
 where (case when inv_before > 0
             then inv_after / inv_before
             else null
             end) between 2.0/3.0 and 3.0/2.0
 order by w_warehouse_name
         ,i_item_id
 limit 110

with my_customers as (

                 cs_item_sk item_sk
          from   catalog_sales
          union all
          select ws_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 ws_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 ws_item_sk item_sk
          from   web_sales

         item,

         and i_class = 'consignment'

         and d_moy = 3
         and d_year = 1999

        sum(ss_ext_sales_price) as revenue

            ,i_item_id
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) < cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                        then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_before
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) >= cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                      then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_after
   from inventory
       ,warehouse
       ,item
       ,date_dim

     and i_item_sk          = inv_item_sk
     and inv_warehouse_sk   = w_warehouse_sk

                    and (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) + INTERVAL '30' day)
   group by w_warehouse_name, i_item_id) x
 where (case when inv_before > 0
             then inv_after / inv_before
             else null
             end) between 2.0/3.0 and 3.0/2.0
 order by w_warehouse_name
         ,i_item_id
 limit 100

         and i_class = 'consignment'
         and c_customer_sk = cs_or_ws_sales.customer_sk
         and d_moy = 3
         and d_year = 1999
 )
 , my_revenue as (
 select c_customer_sk,
        sum(ss_ext_sales_price) as revenue
 from   my_customers,
        store_sales,
        customer_address,
        store,
        date_dim
 where  c_current_addr_sk = ca_address_sk
        and ca_county = s_county
        and ca_state = s_state

                           and  (select distinct d_month_seq+3
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
 group by c_customer_sk
 )
 , segments as
 (select cast((revenue/50) as int) as segment

    and store_sales.ss_store_sk = store.s_store_sk  
    and store_sales.ss_hdemo_sk = household_demographics.hd_demo_sk
    and date_dim.d_dom between 1 and 2 
    and (household_demographics.hd_buy_potential = '>10000' or

    and household_demographics.hd_vehicle_count > 0
    and case when household_demographics.hd_vehicle_count > 0 then 
             household_demographics.hd_dep_count/ household_demographics.hd_vehicle_count else null end > 1
    and date_dim.d_year in (2000,2000+1,2000+2)
    and store.s_county in ('Mobile County','Maverick County','Huron County','Kittitas County')
    group by ss_ticket_number,ss_customer_sk) dj,customer
    where ss_customer_sk = c_customer_sk
      and cnt between 1 and 5
    order by cnt desc, c_last_name asc limit 100

with my_customers as (
 select distinct c_customer_sk
        , c_current_addr_sk
 from   
        ( select cs_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 cs_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 cs_item_sk item_sk
          from   catalog_sales
          union all
          select ws_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 ws_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 ws_item_sk item_sk
          from   web_sales
         ) cs_or_ws_sales,
         item,
         date_dim,
         customer
 where   sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
         and item_sk = i_item_sk
         and i_category = 'Jewelry'
         and i_class = 'consignment'
         and c_customer_sk = cs_or_ws_sales.customer_sk
         and d_moy = 3
         and d_year = 1999
 )
 , my_revenue as (
 select c_customer_sk,
        sum(ss_ext_sales_price) as revenue
 from   my_customers,
        store_sales,
        customer_address,
        store,
        date_dim
 where  c_current_addr_sk = ca_address_sk
        and ca_county = s_county
        and ca_state = s_state
        and ss_sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
        and c_customer_sk = ss_customer_sk
        and d_month_seq between (select distinct d_month_seq+1
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
                           and  (select distinct d_month_seq+3
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
 group by c_customer_sk
 )
 , segments as
 (select cast((revenue/50) as int) as segment
  from   my_revenue
 )
  select  segment*50 as segment_base, segment, count(*) as num_customers
 from segments
 group by segment
 order by segment, num_customers
 limit 100

select  *

            ,i_item_id
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) < cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                        then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_before
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) >= cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                      then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_after
   from inventory
       ,warehouse
       ,item
       ,date_dim
   where i_current_price between 0.99 and 1.49
     and i_item_sk          = inv_item_sk
     and inv_warehouse_sk   = w_warehouse_sk
     and inv_date_sk    = d_date_sk
     and d_date between (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) - INTERVAL '30' day)
                    and (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) + INTERVAL '30' day)
   group by w_warehouse_name, i_item_id) x
 where (case when inv_before > 0
             then inv_after / inv_before
             else null
             end) between 2.0/3.0 and 3.0/2.0
 order by w_warehouse_name
         ,i_item_id
 limit 110

                      else 0 end) as inv_after

 limit 100

            ,i_item_id
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) < cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                        then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_before
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) >= cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                      then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_after
   from inventory
       ,warehouse
       ,item
       ,date_dim
   where i_current_price between 0.99 and 1.49
     and i_item_sk          = inv_item_sk
     and inv_warehouse_sk   = w_warehouse_sk
     and inv_date_sk    = d_date_sk
     and d_date between (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) - INTERVAL '30' day)
                    and (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) + INTERVAL '30' day)
   group by w_warehouse_name, i_item_id) x
 where (case when inv_before > 0
             then inv_after / inv_before
             else null
             end) between 2.0/3.0 and 3.0/2.0
 order by w_warehouse_name
         ,i_item_id
 limit 100

with my_customers as (
 select distinct c_customer_sk
        , c_current_addr_sk
 from   
        ( select cs_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 cs_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 cs_item_sk item_sk
          from   catalog_sales
          union all
          select ws_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 ws_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 ws_item_sk item_sk
          from   web_sales
         ) cs_or_ws_sales,
         item,
         date_dim,
         customer
 where   sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
         and item_sk = i_item_sk
         and i_category = 'Jewelry'
         and i_class = 'consignment'
         and c_customer_sk = cs_or_ws_sales.customer_sk
         and d_moy = 3
         and d_year = 1999
 )
 , my_revenue as (
 select c_customer_sk,
        sum(ss_ext_sales_price) as revenue
 from   my_customers,
        store_sales,
        customer_address,
        store,
        date_dim
 where  c_current_addr_sk = ca_address_sk
        and ca_county = s_county
        and ca_state = s_state
        and ss_sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
        and c_customer_sk = ss_customer_sk
        and d_month_seq between (select distinct d_month_seq+1
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
                           and  (select distinct d_month_seq+3
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
 group by c_customer_sk
 )
 , segments as
 (select cast((revenue/50) as int) as segment
  from   my_revenue
 )
  select  segment, count(*) as num_customers, segment*50 as segment_base
 from segments
 group by segment
 order by segment, num_customers
 limit 100

                 ws_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 ws_item_sk item_sk

         and d_moy = 3
         and d_year = 1999

        sum(ss_ext_sales_price) as revenue
 from   my_customers,
        store_sales,
        customer_address,
        store,
        date_dim
 where  c_current_addr_sk = ca_address_sk

select  *
 from(select w_warehouse_name
            ,i_item_id
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) < cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                        then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_before
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) >= cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                      then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_after
   from inventory
       ,warehouse
       ,item
       ,date_dim
   where i_current_price between 0.99 and 1.49
     and i_item_sk          = inv_item_sk
     and inv_warehouse_sk   = w_warehouse_sk
     and inv_date_sk    = d_date_sk
     and d_date between (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) - INTERVAL '30' day)
                    and (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) + INTERVAL '30' day)
   group by w_warehouse_name, i_item_id) x
 where (case when inv_before > 0
             then inv_after / inv_before
             else null
             end) between 2.0/3.0 and 3.0/2.0
 order by w_warehouse_name
         ,i_item_id
 limit 100

                 ws_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 ws_item_sk item_sk
          from   web_sales

         and d_moy = 3
         and d_year = 1999

        customer_address,

            ,i_item_id
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) < cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                        then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_before
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) >= cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                      then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_after
   from inventory
       ,warehouse
       ,item
       ,date_dim
   where i_current_price between 0.99 and 1.49
     and i_item_sk          = inv_item_sk
     and inv_warehouse_sk   = w_warehouse_sk
     and inv_date_sk    = d_date_sk
     and d_date between (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) - INTERVAL '30' day)
                    and (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) + INTERVAL '30' day)
   group by w_warehouse_name, i_item_id) x
 where (case when inv_before > 0
             then inv_after / inv_before
             else null
             end) between 2.0/3.0 and 3.0/2.0
 order by w_warehouse_name
         ,i_item_id
 limit 100

from

 and     d_year                  = 1999
 and     d_moy                   = 3
 and     cs_bill_addr_sk         = ca_address_sk
 and     ca_gmt_offset           = -6 
 group by i_manufact_id),
 ws as (
 select
          i_manufact_id,sum(ws_ext_sales_price) total_sales
 from
         web_sales,
         date_dim,
         customer_address,
         item
 where
         i_manufact_id               in (select
  i_manufact_id
from
 item

select  
      i_item_desc 
      ,i_category 
      ,i_class 
      ,i_current_price, i_item_id
      ,sum(ws_ext_sales_price) as itemrevenue 
      ,sum(ws_ext_sales_price)*100/sum(sum(ws_ext_sales_price)) over
          (partition by i_class) as revenueratio
from        
        web_sales
            ,item 
            ,date_dim
where 
        ws_item_sk = i_item_sk 
          and i_category in ('Jewelry', 'Sports', 'Books')
          and ws_sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
        and d_date between cast('2001-01-12' as date) 
                                and (cast('2001-01-12' as date) + INTERVAL '30' day)
group by 
        i_item_id
        ,i_item_desc 
        ,i_category
        ,i_class
        ,i_current_price
order by 
        i_category
        ,i_class
        ,i_item_id
        ,i_item_desc
        ,revenueratio
limit 100

select  *
 from(select w_warehouse_name
            ,i_item_id
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) < cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                        then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_before
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) >= cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                      then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_after
   from inventory
       ,warehouse
       ,item
       ,date_dim
   where i_current_price between 0.99 and 1.49
     and i_item_sk          = inv_item_sk
     and inv_warehouse_sk   = w_warehouse_sk
     and inv_date_sk    = d_date_sk
     and d_date between (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) - INTERVAL '30' day)
                    and (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) + INTERVAL '30' day)
   group by w_warehouse_name, i_item_id) x
 where (case when inv_before > 0
             then inv_after / inv_before
             else null
             end) between 2.0/3.0 and 3.0/2.0
 order by w_warehouse_name
         ,i_item_id
 limit 200

select
        cc_call_center_id Call_Center, sum(cr_net_loss) Returns_Loss,
        cc_name Call_Center_Name,
        cc_manager Manager
from         catalog_returns,
        call_center,
        date_dim,
        customer,
        customer_address,
        customer_demographics,
        household_demographics
where
        cr_call_center_sk       = cc_call_center_sk
and     cr_returned_date_sk     = d_date_sk
and     cr_returning_customer_sk= c_customer_sk
and     cd_demo_sk              = c_current_cdemo_sk
and     hd_demo_sk              = c_current_hdemo_sk
and     ca_address_sk           = c_current_addr_sk
and     d_year                  = 1999
and     d_moy                   = 11
and     ( (cd_marital_status       = 'M' and cd_education_status     = 'Unknown')
        or(cd_marital_status       = 'W' and cd_education_status     = 'Advanced Degree'))
and     hd_buy_potential like '0-500%'
and     ca_gmt_offset           = -7
group by cc_call_center_id,cc_name,cc_manager,cd_marital_status,cd_education_status
order by sum(cr_net_loss) desc limit 100

select c_last_name
       ,c_first_name
       ,c_salutation
       ,c_preferred_cust_flag 
       ,ss_ticket_number
       ,cnt from
   (select ss_ticket_number
          ,ss_customer_sk
          ,count(*) cnt
    from store_sales,date_dim,store,household_demographics
    where store_sales.ss_sold_date_sk = date_dim.d_date_sk
    and store_sales.ss_store_sk = store.s_store_sk  
    and store_sales.ss_hdemo_sk = household_demographics.hd_demo_sk
    and date_dim.d_dom between 1 and 2 
    and (household_demographics.hd_buy_potential = '>10000' or
         household_demographics.hd_buy_potential = 'Unknown')
    and household_demographics.hd_vehicle_count > 0
    and case when household_demographics.hd_vehicle_count > 0 then 
             household_demographics.hd_dep_count/ household_demographics.hd_vehicle_count else null end > 1
    and date_dim.d_year in (2000,2000+1,2000+2)
    and store.s_county in ('Mobile County','Maverick County','Huron County','Kittitas County')
    group by ss_ticket_number,ss_customer_sk) dj,customer
    where ss_customer_sk = c_customer_sk
      and cnt between 1 and 5
    order by cnt desc, c_last_name asc limit 100

with my_customers as (
 select distinct c_customer_sk
        , c_current_addr_sk
 from   
        ( select cs_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 cs_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 cs_item_sk item_sk
          from   catalog_sales
          union all
          select ws_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 ws_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 ws_item_sk item_sk
          from   web_sales
         ) cs_or_ws_sales,
         item,
         date_dim,
         customer
 where   sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
         and item_sk = i_item_sk
         and i_category = 'Jewelry'
         and i_class = 'consignment'
         and c_customer_sk = cs_or_ws_sales.customer_sk
         and d_moy = 3
         and d_year = 1999
 )
 , my_revenue as (
 select c_customer_sk,
        sum(ss_ext_sales_price) as revenue
 from   my_customers,
        store_sales,
        customer_address,
        store,
        date_dim
 where  c_current_addr_sk = ca_address_sk
        and ca_county = s_county

                      else 0 end) as inv_after

with my_customers as (

 from   
        ( select cs_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 cs_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 cs_item_sk item_sk
          from   catalog_sales
          union all
          select ws_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 ws_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 ws_item_sk item_sk
          from   web_sales
         ) cs_or_ws_sales,
         item,
         date_dim,
         customer
 where   sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
         and item_sk = i_item_sk
         and i_category = 'Jewelry'
         and i_class = 'consignment'
         and c_customer_sk = cs_or_ws_sales.customer_sk
         and d_moy = 3
         and d_year = 1999
 )
 , my_revenue as (
 select c_customer_sk,
        sum(ss_ext_sales_price) as revenue
 from   my_customers,
        store_sales,
        customer_address,
        store,
        date_dim
 where  c_current_addr_sk = ca_address_sk
        and ca_county = s_county
        and ca_state = s_state
        and ss_sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
        and c_customer_sk = ss_customer_sk
        and d_month_seq between (select distinct d_month_seq+1
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
                           and  (select distinct d_month_seq+3
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
 group by c_customer_sk
 )
 , segments as
 (select cast((revenue/50) as int) as segment
  from   my_revenue
 )
  select  segment*50 as segment_base, segment, count(*) as num_customers
 from segments
 group by segment
 order by segment, num_customers
 limit 100

select  *
 from(select w_warehouse_name
            ,i_item_id
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) < cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                        then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_before
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) >= cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                      then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_after
   from inventory
       ,warehouse
       ,item
       ,date_dim
   where i_current_price between 0.99 and 1.49
     and i_item_sk          = inv_item_sk
     and inv_warehouse_sk   = w_warehouse_sk
     and inv_date_sk    = d_date_sk
     and d_date between (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) - INTERVAL '30' day)
                    and (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) + INTERVAL '30' day)
   group by w_warehouse_name, i_item_id) x
 where (case when inv_before > 0
             then inv_after / inv_before
             else null
             end) between 2.0/3.0 and 3.0/2.0
 order by w_warehouse_name
         ,i_item_id
 limit 200

with my_customers as (
 select distinct c_customer_sk
        , c_current_addr_sk
 from   
        ( select cs_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 cs_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 cs_item_sk item_sk
          from   catalog_sales
          union all
          select ws_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 ws_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 ws_item_sk item_sk
          from   web_sales
         ) cs_or_ws_sales,
         item,
         date_dim,
         customer
 where   sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
         and item_sk = i_item_sk
         and i_category = 'Jewelry'
         and i_class = 'consignment'
         and c_customer_sk = cs_or_ws_sales.customer_sk
         and d_moy = 3
         and d_year = 1999
 )
 , my_revenue as (
 select c_customer_sk,
        sum(ss_ext_sales_price) as revenue
 from   my_customers,
        store_sales,
        customer_address,
        store,
        date_dim
 where  c_current_addr_sk = ca_address_sk
        and ca_county = s_county
        and ca_state = s_state
        and ss_sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
        and c_customer_sk = ss_customer_sk
        and d_month_seq between (select distinct d_month_seq+1
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
                           and  (select distinct d_month_seq+3
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
 group by c_customer_sk
 )
 , segments as
 (select cast((revenue/50) as int) as segment
  from   my_revenue
 )
  select  segment, count(*) as num_customers, segment*50 as segment_base
 from segments
 group by segment
 order by segment, num_customers
 limit 100

with my_customers as (
 select distinct c_customer_sk
        , c_current_addr_sk
 from   
        ( select cs_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 cs_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 cs_item_sk item_sk
          from   catalog_sales
          union all
          select ws_sold_date_sk sold_date_sk,
                 ws_bill_customer_sk customer_sk,
                 ws_item_sk item_sk
          from   web_sales
         ) cs_or_ws_sales,
         item,
         date_dim,
         customer
 where   sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
         and item_sk = i_item_sk
         and i_category = 'Jewelry'
         and i_class = 'consignment'
         and c_customer_sk = cs_or_ws_sales.customer_sk
         and d_moy = 3
         and d_year = 1999
 )
 , my_revenue as (
 select c_customer_sk,
        sum(ss_ext_sales_price) as revenue
 from   my_customers,
        store_sales,
        customer_address,
        store,
        date_dim
 where  c_current_addr_sk = ca_address_sk
        and ca_county = s_county
        and ca_state = s_state
        and ss_sold_date_sk = d_date_sk
        and c_customer_sk = ss_customer_sk
        and d_month_seq between (select distinct d_month_seq+1
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
                           and  (select distinct d_month_seq+3
                                 from   date_dim where d_year = 1999 and d_moy = 3)
 group by c_customer_sk
 )
 , segments as
 (select cast((revenue/50) as int) as segment
  from   my_revenue
 )
  select  segment, segment*50 as segment_base, count(*) as num_customers
 from segments
 group by segment
 order by segment, num_customers
 limit 120

                        then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_before
            ,sum(case when (cast(d_date as date) >= cast ('1998-04-08' as date))
                      then inv_quantity_on_hand
                      else 0 end) as inv_after
   from inventory
       ,warehouse
       ,item
       ,date_dim

     and i_item_sk          = inv_item_sk
     and inv_warehouse_sk   = w_warehouse_sk

                    and (cast ('1998-04-08' as date) + INTERVAL '30' day)
   group by w_warehouse_name, i_item_id) x
 where (case when inv_before > 0
             then inv_after / inv_before
             else null
             end) between 2.0/3.0 and 3.0/2.0
 order by w_warehouse_name
         ,i_item_id
 limit 110

            ,i_item_id
